    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Based on the seven assessed credibility factors and the available validation evidence, the CFD model is accepted for the VAD hemolysis prediction COU. Six factors remain unassessed and represent acknowledged gaps; however, the assessment team determined that the available evidence is sufficient for the intended decision context. The model demonstrates reasonable agreement with experimental hemolysis data across the operating range.",
